 2' \u2013 a.k.a. the suspect in the white hat, the one authorities apparently saw drop a bomb-laden backpack in security footages, and the one currently being pursued by police:\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name = cnn-timeline-2013-04-22>{{Cite news\n| author = \n| url = http://edition.cnn.com/2013/04/21/us/tamerlan-tsarnaev-timeline/index.html\n| title = Timeline: A look at Tamerlan Tsarnaev's past\n| date = April 22, 2013\n| website = [[CNN]]\n| location = Atlanta, GA, US\n| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140203152157/http://edition.cnn.com/2013/04/21/us/tamerlan-tsarnaev-timeline/index.html\n| archive-date = February 3, 2014\n| url-status = live\n| access-date = May 3, 2015\n| quote = Hours later, investigators reveal that he and his 19-year-old younger brother are the marathon bombing suspects.\n}}</ref>\n\n<!-- <ref name = globe-injured-2013-04-24>{{cite news|last=Kotz|first=Deborah|title=Injury toll from Marathon bombs reduced to 264|url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/lifestyle/health-wellness/2013/04/23/number-injured-marathon-bombing-revised-downward/NRpaz5mmvGquP7KMA6XsIK/story.html|newspaper=The Boston Globe|date=April 24, 2013}}</ref>\n -->\n<ref name = star-zubeidat-2013-04-28>{{cite news|url=https://www.thestar.com/news/world/2013/04/28/boston_marathon_bombings_suspects_mother_zubeidat_says_she_found_faith_not_terrorism.html|title=Boston Marathon bombings: Suspects' mother Zubeidat says she found faith, not terrorism|newspaper=The Star|date=April 28, 2013|accessdate=May 6, 2013|location=Toronto}}</ref>\n\n<!-- <ref name = cbs-dandt-2013-04-23>{{cite news|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/dzhokhar-and-tamerlan-a-profile-of-the-tsarnaev-brothers/ |title=Dzhokhar and Tamerlan: A Profile of the Tsarnaev Brothers |date=April 23, 2013 |website=[[CBS News]]}}</ref> -->\n\n<ref name = cnn-indictment-2013-06-27><!--see point 39 in indictment-->{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/interactive/2013/06/us/tsarnaev-indictment/index.html |date=June 27, 2013 |title=Indict