reporter.com/news/dorian-award-nominations-favourite-pose-lead-1173113|title='The Favourite,' 'Pose,' 'Killing Eve' Lead Dorian Award Nominations|last=Kilkenny|first=Katie|work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|date= 3 January 2019|accessdate=3 January 2019|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190104060713/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/dorian-award-nominations-favourite-pose-lead-1173113|archivedate=4 January 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Producers Guild of America Award]]\n| [[Producers Guild of America Awards 2018|Outstanding Producer of Live Entertainment & Talk Television]]\n| {{nom}}\n! style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"PGA18\">{{cite web|url=https://www.thewrap.com/producers-guild-awards-nominations-include-roma-black-panther-a-star-is-born-and-also-crazy-rich-asians/|title=Producers Guild Awards Nominations Include \u2018Roma,\u2019 \u2018Black Panther,\u2019 \u2018A Star Is Born\u2019 \u2013 and Also \u2018Crazy Rich Asians\u2019|work=[[TheWrap]]|last=Pond|first=Steve|date=4 January 2019|accessdate=4 January 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190104233506/https://www.thewrap.com/producers-guild-awards-nominations-include-roma-black-panther-a-star-is-born-and-also-crazy-rich-asians/|archive-date=4 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"|[[NAACP Image Awards]]\n| [[NAACP Image Award for Outstanding Talk Series|Outstanding Talk Series]]\n| {{nom}}\n! style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"4\"|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/02/naacp-image-awards-2019-nominees-list-film-tv-music-books-black-panther-1202556258/|title=NAACP Image Awards Nominees: \u2018Black Panther\u2019, \u2018Beale Street\u2019, Netflix, HBO Top List|last=Hipes|first=Patrick|work=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=February 13, 2019|accessdate=February 13, 2019|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://deadline.com/2019/02/naacp-image-awards-2019-nominees-list-film-tv-music-books-black-panther-1202556258/|archivedate=February 13, 2019}}</ref>\n