ter |date=12 March 2017|work=[[Eyewitness News (South Africa)|Eyewitness News]]|accessdate=12 March 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130420011814/http://ewn.co.za/2017/03/13/noah-wins-fave-african-star-at-nickelodeon-kids-choice-awards|archivedate=12 March 2017|df=}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[GLAAD Media Award]]\n| [[28th GLAAD Media Awards|Outstanding Talk Show Episode]]\n| {{won}}\n! style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ew.com/news/2017/05/06/debra-messing-daily-show-glaad-media-awards/|title=Debra Messing, 'Daily Show' among winners at GLAAD Media Awards|first=Derek|last=Lawrence|work=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|date=6 May 2017|accessdate=7 May 2017 |url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130420011814/https://ew.com/news/2017/05/06/debra-messing-daily-show-glaad-media-awards/ |archivedate=6 May 2017|df=}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[MTV Movie & TV Awards]]\n| [[2017 MTV Movie & TV Awards|Best Host]]\n| {{won}}\n! style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/3000426/2017-mtv-movie-tv-awards-nominations/|title=Here Are Your 2017 MTV Movie & TV Awards Nominations: See The Full List|last=Bell|first=Crystal|date=6 April 2017|publisher=[[MTV News]]|accessdate=6 April 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130420011814/http://www.mtv.com/news/3000426/2017-mtv-movie-tv-awards-nominations/ |archivedate=6 April 2017|df=}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award]]\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Short Form Variety Series|Outstanding Short Form Variety Series]]\n| ''The Daily Show with Trevor Noah \u2013 Between the Scenes''\n| {{won}}\n! style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"Emmys\">{{cite web|url=https://www.emmys.com/bios/trevor-noah|title=Trevor Noah|publisher=[[Academy of Television Arts & Sciences]]/[[National Academy of Television Arts and Sciences]]|accessdate=13 September 2017|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/672es9SRJ?url=https://www.emmys.com/bios/trevor-noah|