st Host]]\n| {{nom}}\n! style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/3124121/2019-mtv-movie-tv-awards-nominations-list/|title=2019 MTV Movie & TV Awards Nominations: See the Full List|last=Ball|first=Crystal|date=May 14, 2019|accessdate=May 14, 2019|publisher=[[MTV News]]|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220104835/http://www.mtv.com/news/3124121/2019-mtv-movie-tv-awards-nominations-list/|archivedate=May 14, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Primetime Emmy Award]]\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Variety Talk Series|Outstanding Variety Talk Series]]\n| {{nom}}\n! style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"2\"|<ref name=\"Emmys\"/>\n|-\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Interactive Program|Outstanding Interactive Program]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[People's Choice Awards]]\n| [[45th People's Choice Awards|The Nighttime Talk Show of 2019]]\n| {{nom}}\n! style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"PeoplesChoice\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.eonline.com/shows/peoples_choice_awards/news/1068008/2019-people-s-choice-awards-complete-list-of-nominees |title=2019 People's Choice Awards: Complete List of Nominees |last=Klemme |first=Kelsey |website=[[E! Online]] |date=September 4, 2019 |access-date=September 4, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190904180520/https://www.eonline.com/shows/peoples_choice_awards/news/1068008/2019-people-s-choice-awards-complete-list-of-nominees |archive-date=September 4, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"7\" | 2020\n| [[Critics' Choice Television Award]]\n| Best Comedy Special\n| ''Trevor Noah: Son of Patricia''\n| {{nom}}\n! style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/12/critics-choice-nominations-film-tv-nominees-list-1202803785/|title=\u2018The Irishman\u2019,\u2019Once Upon A Time In Hollywood\u2019 Lead Critics Choice Nominations; Netflix Dominates With 61 Nods In Movies And TV|last=Hammond|first=Pete|website=Deadline Hollywo